msgctxt "sn56.29:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga "
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Pariññeyyasutta "
msgstr "29. Should Be Completely Understood "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.436, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.29:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four noble truths. "

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.3"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ—"
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni. "
msgstr "These are the four noble truths. "

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ atthi ariyasaccaṃ pariññeyyaṃ, atthi ariyasaccaṃ pahātabbaṃ, atthi ariyasaccaṃ sacchikātabbaṃ, atthi ariyasaccaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ. "
msgstr "Of these four noble truths, there is one to be completely understood, one to be given up, one to be realized, and one to be developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.29:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, ariyasaccaṃ pariññeyyaṃ? "
msgstr "And which noble truth should be completely understood? "

msgctxt "sn56.29:2.2"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasaccaṃ pariññeyyaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ pahātabbaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ sacchikātabbaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ. "
msgstr "The noble truth of suffering should be completely understood. The noble truth of the origin of suffering should be given up. The noble truth of the cessation of suffering should be realized. The noble truth of the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering should be developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.29:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.29:3.2"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

